<%= semantic_form_for @userid do |f| %>


    <div id="main"style="color:black">
<table  style="width: 100%">
  <tr>    
    <th style="width:70%">Field</th>
    <th style="width:30">Value</th>
  </tr>

<tr><td>
Please provide us with a unique idenfification name. This will be used by the system to identify you at all times. The namee must only contain alphabetic characters and numbers; it must NOT contain any special characters or spaces. It can be of any length. Avoid using your forename as it likely to have already been taken. <b>Mandatory</b>
</td><td> 
<%= f.input :userid,:input_html => { :required => true,:size => 35 }%> </td></tr>
<tr><td>
Select the syndicate with which you wish to transcribe 
</td><td>
<%= f.input :syndicate,  {:as => :select,:include_blank => true,
          :required => true, :collection => @syndicates, :size => 15 ,:required => true } %> </td></tr>
<tr><td>
Your forename or given name
</td><td>
<%= f.input :person_forename,:input_html => { :size => 35 }%></td></tr>
<tr><td>Your surname</td><td>
<%= f.input :person_surname,:input_html => { :size => 35 }%></td></tr>
<tr><td>Your email address</td><td>
<%= f.input :email_address,:input_html => { :required => true,:size => 35 } %></td></tr>
<tr><td>
Please provide us with you physical location, i.e. Country.
</td><td>
<%= f.input :address,:input_html => { :size => 35 }%></td></tr>
<tr><td>
Please provide us with a telephone number in case we need to contact you.
</td><td>
<%= f.input :telephone_number,:input_html => { :size => 35 }%></td></tr>
<tr><td>
Please tell us if you have a fiche reader.
</td><td>
<%= f.input :fiche_reader, {:as => :select,  :collection => [true,false],:include_blank => false, :size => 35}%></td></tr>
<tr><td>
Please read the <%= link_to 'participation agreement', places_path%> and confirm that you accept these terms. PLEASE NOTE THE AGREEMENT IS NOT THERE YET
</td><td>
<%= f.input :transcription_agreement, {:as => :check_boxes,  :collection => [true], :include_blank => false, :required => true,:size => 35}%></td></tr>

</table>
<p><b>After submitting this form you will be redirected to the home page and will receive an email that contains a link to complete the registration process. Click on that link (or copy and paste it into you browser addres window) WITHIN 24HRS. </b></p>

 
    <%= f.action :submit, :as => :input, :label => 'Register Transcriber' %>
   <% end %>
</div>


